data.description: Spacious mid-century ranch home on deep, half-acre lot ITB in historic Madonna Acres, and nearby Mordecai and Oakwood historic districts; super close to downtown! Charming original mosaic tile style porch in front, large inviting entryway, open concept kitchen / family room, plus a formal living room with tons of natural light, large bedrooms, laundry room; Gorgeous oak hardwood floors throughout home!  Sliding glass door leads out to the large patio and enormous fenced backyard.  Lots of storage spaces. Recently updated kitchen with quartz counters, waterfall island, stainless steel appliances, gas range w/ hood vent.  Partially-updated bathrooms with some desirable vintage finishes preserved!  Wood-burning masonry fireplace in family room has a cozy sitting-height hearth.  This home is just all around wonderful - must see!! See agent remarks for closing cost / rate buy-down assistance offered!
